title: NFL ATL: Week 3 recap
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 3 recap
description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling breakdown all of the Week 3 action and get you ready for the “Monday Night Football” matchup between the Oakland Raiders and Denver Broncos. Don’t miss the analysis and key takeaways from each game. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
